<seg id="352">His conclusions remained unknown until they were redeemed by the group from USPlast year.</seg>
<seg id="353">The São Paulo physicists arrived at the same result as Dirac with a very simple conceptual model, equivalent to an electron immersed in a vacuum, vibrating on the tip of a spring.</seg>
