<seg id="455">Team</seg>
<seg id="456">With so many protagonists on stage, teamwork has become fundamental.</seg>
<seg id="457">In this type of spectacle creation is divided up both by the choreographer and by the specialists in technology and the dancer, a co-creator in real time, who very often controls the various media on stage, during the presentation.</seg>
