<seg id="1701">The pact between science and the government signed at the end of the Second World War and founded on the idea of the dichotomy between basic and applied research has lapsed.</seg>
<seg id="1702">A new model of the relationship between science and technology must be conceived in order to reestablish the dialogue between the communities of the scientists and the politicians.</seg>
